[{"url_token": "jiu-zhi-dao-chi-58-84", "headline": "六小龄童", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "744299304", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "744299304", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "说得好，但我选择燃油车", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "就知道吃", "author_id": "be2ff58faac72315ce2ab3c3e5eb747f", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "long-shan-tang-20", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "744204819", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "744204819", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "开的多的能把差价找回来，开的少的，还是自然吸气的吧，否则平白多了一套系统损坏的风险。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "龙山堂", "author_id": "11a5cf92cfb7a70f76fbb2e8b367ecd4", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "langfeileon", "headline": "互联网", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "698119181", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "698119181", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>想问问，一、电动车电池衰减这么厉害，带来的是电动车的贬值，难道电动车打算开到报废么？二、电动车越来越多，可是停车场的充电桩就那么几个，难道轮流排队充电耗时间么，好吧，也只能这样了。。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "吃瓜路人甲", "author_id": "60656a9d6b6fca7f9b6a69069c35c136", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "jckyo", "headline": "专业编制外人员，专注打杂15年，资深皮毛……", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "692761605", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "692761605", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有条件拥有桩，必须买电动！", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "文一刀", "author_id": "57efff26e9ef2610624befa6859d33a4", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "han-shuo-80-90", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "691687502", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "691687502", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很明显，即便电动别的经济性再好......也不适合作为家庭第一部车......因为没办法上高速，也没办法远距离旅游出差......如果是小区不允许安充电桩，公用电桩的价格也会缩小使用的价差......还有各种不方便......<br><br><br> 最关键的是电动车其实耐用性压根比不上汽油车...特别是电池，答主知道几年后缩水成啥样子了不？车企的电池质保并不包括电池容量衰减......请参考手机的电池质保，掉的妈都不认识了还属于正常使用......这个属性注定了只能通勤和短途代步，并且电动车的保值率真是惨不忍睹，有这个想法我为什么我为什么不买个混合动力......不担心充电焦虑症......又不担心二手车价亏到姥姥家，混合动力车现在日系都做到5L以下了朋友，一公里才3毛钱不到......一年使用费也就比你说的电动车贵2000，更何况现在电动车其实是比混动车贵的......看看双擎的雷凌和亚洲龙，还有混动雅阁才多少钱......", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "人无贬基", "author_id": "ebdbea62ba44ec9ed9ab3f32ae487d15", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "Gwanlap", "headline": "雷風恆 君子以立不易方", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "691573026", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "691573026", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "同配置的电动车至少比汽油车贵10%。你说多长时间才能赚回油费？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "君立", "author_id": "36a49f042f0c337d91bfc4226cba05f7", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "qi-lin-xi-90", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "690507657", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "690507657", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "同样十几万的车 汽油车开一年二手车掉价一万 电动车掉价三万", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "柏毅", "author_id": "caf7fa49eca2cdc8ffd2b3ee2fd6fe3a", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "xiao-peng-qi-che", "headline": "未来出行探索者", "is_advertiser": true, "comment_id": "690525119", "reply_comment_id": "690507657", "reply_root_comment_id": "690507657", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>所有车，开出门就是打八折，15万的车，无论是燃油车还是电动车，都不可能掉价一万的呀。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "小鹏汽车", "author_id": "57c22a016e42df5a4f36be0732187a4a", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "guang-de-yuan", "headline": "口腔医生", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "688189116", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "688189116", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "第一，现在的车油耗没那么高。我刚买的，科鲁兹，家用够了，油耗平均4.7。油价一般活动加，6.1左右。那么一个月就是4.7*6.1*15=430.1。<br>第二，电动车，很多打出换电瓶不要钱，但是，换电瓶的时候，还要换相关的配件，很贵的。基本上一个电瓶最多撑两三年，基本上都是一年就换，不然，真的没法用。<br>第三，电动车<br>随时都要注意电量，尤其是开空调的时候，真的太费电。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "光的远", "author_id": "8299c994f5e03840e2de33da370a1241", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "xiao-peng-qi-che", "headline": "未来出行探索者", "is_advertiser": true, "comment_id": "690525706", "reply_comment_id": "688189116", "reply_root_comment_id": "688189116", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>你说错啦鹏友，电动车开空调真不费电，开暖气比较费电，可以参考：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/66748760\" class=\"internal\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/66</span><span class=\"invisible\">748760</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "小鹏汽车", "author_id": "57c22a016e42df5a4f36be0732187a4a", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "pony-39-68", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "675071882", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "675071882", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "如果有跑长途需求呢？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "西服中长款", "author_id": "4a317d53a935c9a8e5c75c993ba66695", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "xiao-peng-qi-che", "headline": "未来出行探索者", "is_advertiser": true, "comment_id": "675244231", "reply_comment_id": "675071882", "reply_root_comment_id": "675071882", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>经常跑长途，不要买电动车，就这么真实。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "小鹏汽车", "author_id": "57c22a016e42df5a4f36be0732187a4a", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "yu-shan-31-70", "headline": "我就想站着把钱给挣了！", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "672390668", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "672390668", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我买的奇瑞小蚂蚁，差价？6万的新车你跟我谈差价？别的不说，自动挡a000的小车这个档的有多少？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "非也", "author_id": "0375cb46d15e4fb193c37435f8e362bd", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]